       exe-exp-zv3-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione file area generica                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "mtv "               to   f-xxx-are              .
           move      "zv3 "               to   f-xxx-nam              .
           move      "std_mtv_zv3"        to   f-xxx-npe              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
